                <head>27. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On February 13, 1961, Ambassador <persName corresp="#p_TLEJ1">Thompson</persName>
                    testified before the Senate Foreign Relations Committee for over 2 hours on
                    conditions in the Soviet Union, U.S.-Soviet relations, and Soviet policy around
                    the world. For a transcript of the proceedings, see <hi rend="italic">Executive
                        Sessions of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee (Historical Series),
                        1961,</hi> pages 135-178.</p>
            </div>
